                    <physDesc>
                        <objectDesc>
                            <supportDesc>
                                <support><p>Rectilinear grey limestone plaque, missing left edge and large part of lower left corner. Abrasion in top right corner. Traces of (modern?) mortar and modern paint on sides. Rear is flat.</p>
                                    <material ana="#material.stone.limestone" ref="http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/material/lod/66.html">limestone</material>
